ROOT CAUSE: UNUSED WIRES NOT LISTED IN WIRE LIST AND NO INSTRUCTION ON PRINT ABOUT WHAT TO DO WITH THEM.  SOLUTION: ADD UNUSED WIRES TO WIRE LIST AS “NO CONNECTION,” ADD NOTE TO WRAP UNUSED WIRES WITH HEATSHRINK.
